quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,"Okubonaabona okwamaanyi kugenda kubeera ku buli muntu atambuza engambo, ageya banne n'abaggya obumogo"
  104,2,Oyo akungaanya ebyo bugagga n’abituuma
  104,3,Alowooza nti eby'obugaggabye byakumukuumira ku nsi obugenderevu
  104,4,"Nedda, ajja kukanyugwa mu muliro oguyitibwa “Hutwama”"
  104,5,Ye omanyi “Hutwama” kye ki
  104,6,"(Hutwama) muliro gwa Katonda omukume, ogubumbujja"
  104,7,Ogwo ogwokya negutuukira ddala ku mitima
  104,8,Mazima ddala omuliro ogwo (Hutwama) ku bantu abo (abogeddwaako) gugenda kubabuutikira
  104,9,Mu midumu emiwanvu